Проверяем состояние ответа на вопрос Если есть корректный ответ - принят если есть комменты под вопросом - отвечен если комментов нет - не отвечен ну и если тип поста не вопрос - то не является вопросом

query.sql: Select *, YEAR(Created) as Year, TO_CHAR( TO_TIMESTAMP(CAST(Created AS VARCHAR(4000)), 'YYYY-MM-DD'), 'MON-YYYY') as MonthYear, CAST(CONVERT(char(6), Created, 112) AS int) as MonthYearNum, TO_DATE(CAST(Created AS VARCHAR(4000)), 'YYYY-MM-DD') as FullDate, case when Instr(Lang,'en',1)>0 then 1 else 0 END as CountEN, case when Instr(Lang,'es',1)>0 then 1 else 0 END as CountES, case when Instr(Lang,'ja',1)>0 then 1 else 0 END as CountJA, case when Instr(Lang,'pt',1)>0 then 1 else 0 END as CountPT, case when Instr(Lang,'zh-hant',1)>0 then 1 else 0 END as CountZH_HANT, case when Instr(Lang,'fr',1)>0 then 1 else 0 END as CountFR from Community.Member as cm

query.sql: select *, TO_CHAR( Created, 'MON-YYYY') as MonthYear, CAST(TO_CHAR( Created, 'YYYYMM') as INT) as MonthYearNum, Year( Created ) as YearNum, TO_DATE(CAST(Created AS VARCHAR(4000)), 'YYYY-MM-DD') as FullDate, CASE WHEN Instr(Tags, 'Caché', 1) > 0 then 'Cache' WHEN Instr(Tags, 'Atelier', 1) > 0 then 'Atelier' WHEN Instr(Tags, 'Ensemble', 1) > 0 then 'Ensemble' WHEN Instr(Tags, 'HealthShare', 1) > 0 then 'HealthShare' WHEN Instr(Tags, 'iKnow', 1) > 0 then 'iKnow' WHEN Instr(Tags, 'InterSystems IRIS', 1) > 0 then 'InterSystems IRIS' END as TagsMajor, CASE WHEN PostType = 'Article' then 1 else 0 END as CountArticle, case when PostType = 'Question' then 1 else 0 END as CountQuestions, case when PostType = 'Announcement' then 1 else 0 END as CountAnnouncement, case when PostType = 'Discussion' then 1 else 0 END as CountDiscussion, case when Instr(Tags,'Caché',1)>0 then 1 else 0 END as CountTagCache, case when Instr(Tags,'InterSystems IRIS,',1)>0 then 1 else 0 END as CountTagIRIS, case when Instr(Tags,'HealthShare',1)>0 then 1 else 0 END as CountTagHealthShare, case when Instr(Tags,'Ensemble',1)>0 then 1 else 0 END as CountTagEnsemble, case when Lang = 'en' then 1 else 0 END as CountEnTotal, case when Lang = 'es' then 1 else 0 END as CountEsTotal, case when Lang = 'ja' then 1 else 0 END as CountJpTotal, case when Lang = 'zh-hant' then 1 else 0 END as CountCNTotal, case when Lang = 'pt' then 1 else 0 END as CountPtTotal, case when Lang = 'fr' then 1 else 0 END as CountFrTotal, case when HasCorrectAnswer = 1 then 'Accepted' when (CommentsAmount = 0 and PostType = 'Question') then 'Unanswered' when (CommentsAmount > 0 and PostType = 'Question') then 'Answered' else 'NonQuestion' END as QuestionType from Community.Post as cp WHERE deleted = 0 and published = 1 and PostType != 'Digest'

column.name: Tagss
column.sql: CASE WHEN Instr(Tags, 'Caché', 1) > 0 then 'Cache' WHEN Instr(Tags, 'Atelier', 1) > 0 then 'Atelier' WHEN Instr(Tags, 'Ensemble', 1) > 0 then 'Ensemble' WHEN Instr(Tags, 'HealthShare', 1) > 0 then 'HealthShare' WHEN Instr(Tags, 'iKnow', 1) > 0 then 'iKnow' WHEN Instr(Tags, 'InterSystems IRIS', 1) > 0 then 'InterSystems IRIS' END

column.name: Day
column.sql: Day(Created)

column.name: Lang
column.sql: case when Lang = 'en' then 'EN' when Lang = 'es' then 'ES' when Lang = 'ja' then 'JA' when Lang = 'pt' then 'PT' when Lang = 'zh-hant' then 'CN' when Lang = 'fr' then 'FR' END

column.name: WeekYear
column.sql: DATEPART(week, Created)

query.sql: select hv.*, CAST(TO_CHAR( DateOfData, 'YYYYMM') as Int) as MonthYearNum, TO_CHAR( DateOfData, 'MON-YYYY') as MonthYear, Year( DateOfData ) as YearNum from History.Views hv LEFT JOIN Community.Post as cp on hv.Post = cp.ID WHERE cp.deleted = 0 and cp.published = 1 and cp.PostType != 'Digest'

column.name: MonthYearNum

column.name: MonthYear
column.sql: TO_CHAR( TO_TIMESTAMP(CAST(DateOfData AS VARCHAR(4000)), 'YYYY-MM-DD'), 'MON-YYYY')
